Citations Affected: IC 4-21.5; IC 6-1.1; IC 20-19; IC 20-24;
IC 20-25.7; IC 20-26; IC 20-32.
Synopsis: Various education matters. Requires the department of
education (department) to: (1) compile a list of business and industry
partners that provide guaranteed incentives to high school students who
earn the honors employment plus seal; and (2) publish the list on the
department's website. Provides that, in addition to conditions
established in current law to convert an existing public elementary or
(Continued next page)
Effective: Upon passage; July 1, 2026.
Rogers, Raatz, Donato, Buchanan,
Doriot
